## 🚀 Deployment

### Frontend
- Build: `npm run build` (static export to `/out`)
- Hosting: Cloudflare Pages (auto-deploys on main push)
- URL: https://lazygolfing.com

### Backend
- Build: `npm run build` (TypeScript → JavaScript)
- Runtime: PM2 on Ubuntu VM (192.168.1.40)
- Service: `lg-api`
- URL: https://api.lazygolfing.com
- Critical: Must run `npm run build` BEFORE `pm2 restart`

### Database
- PostgreSQL on VM (Docker)
- Backups: Daily at 2:00 AM UTC
- Retention: 30 days auto-cleanup

